				<td colspan="2"><span>1. Go someplace with lots and lots of non-spellcasting darkblue mobs and pull yourself a righteous train.
<br />
2. Sing DA song and let the train catch you.
<br />
3. Let them beat on you until DA almost wears off ... and GET OUT OF THERE!
<br />
4. Repeat steps 2-4 until you max Defense.</span></td>
